Package gw.api.json.schema

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JsonSchema
    Runtime representation of a JSON Schema file.
    JsonSchemaDefinition
    A single type definition within a JSON Schema file.
    JsonSchemaItems
    Represents the "items" property of a JsonSchemaProperty definition.
    JsonSchemaProperty
    Represents a single property delcaration from a JSON Schema file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FormattedJsonType
    Simple value type class that combines the notion of the underlying native JSON type, a format, and a further Guidewire-specific type.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    NativeJsonType
    Represents the native JSON data types
